---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 301
  - Title: Brihad-Âranyaka Upanishad
    Location: I iv 14
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Necessity of Submission
---
Verily, that which is Law (dharma) is truth. Therefore they say of a
man who speaks the Supra truth, ‘He speaks the Law,’ or of a man who
speaks the Law, ‘He speaks the truth.’ Verily, Introd.  both these are
the same thing.
